metadata.name: PAPEPER TOY
metadata.description:
PAPEPER TOY portrays Pepe the Frog by Matt Furie in its original form inspired by the comic "Boy's Club" from the distant years of 2008/2009. Even today, Pepe continues to play a fundamental role in internet culture, particularly within the NFT world, generating ever-growing interest and bringing together numerous enthusiasts in dedicated sub-communities.

PAPEPER TOY serves as gateway to the "Culture Toys" ecosystem. It is the initial point of access for collectors and enthusiasts. After the open edition a burn/redeem event will be held, allowing owners to burn their toy for the next drops in the collection
